               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Malkǝʾa Gabra Manfas Qǝddus “Image of Gabra Manfas Qǝddus” (fols.
                     1r-15r), incomplete.&#xD; II) Unidentified hymn about the miracles of Gabra
                     Manfas Qǝddus (?) (15v-19v)&#xD; III) Mǝśṭira ṣǝgeyāt “The Mystery of the
                     Flowers” (fols. 20r-37v), incomplete&#xD; IV) Malkǝʾa kidāna mǝḥrat “Image of
                     the Covenant of Mercy” (fols. 38r-43v)&#xD; V) Malkǝʾa ʾIyasus “Image of Jesus”
                     (fols.44r-45v), incomplete&#xD; VI) Unidentified prayer (?) (fols. 46r-49v),
                     incomplete&#xD; VII) Commemorative notice and ʿarke-hymn for the 23rd of
                     Miyāzyā dedicated to St Roch (Roqo) (fols. 50r-53r) &#xD; VIII) Unidentified
                     prayer (?) (fols. 53r-57r).</summary>
